title: RAM Manager Pro v8.0.10
description:
RAM Manager is application which optimizes the RAM of all Android devices and keep the best balance between enough free memory and running applications. This application reduces lags for a purpose of increasing speed of your device. RAM Manager is the best solution for all who have problem with the free memory, with the multitasking, with slow swapping between applications, with low performance or just want to improve the performance in all directions. You can simply boost speed of your device simply by selecting specific profile which you actually need. 

Pro Features:

- No ads.
- All features.
- Faster support.
- More frequent updates
